summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Human Services Program establishing 1990 expenditure allowances for certain youth, emergency shelter, food, employment, advocacy, medical services, and community services in the 1990 budgets of the Department of Human Resources, the Human Services Strategic Planning Office, the Department of Community Development, the Department of Parks and Recreation, and the Seattle-King County Department of Public Health by the reduction, reappropriation, and transfer of amounts previously appropriated in the 1990 budget.
